<taxonomicName id="76AAE10711A63CDD033EBE4B2ECDA6FA" genus="X." lsidName="X. mexicana" pageId="0" pageNumber="13" rank="species" species="mexicana">X. mexicana</taxonomicName>
by nucleotide position characters in the ITS sequence as shown in Table 2.
</paragraph>
